message: Hi Bob, I have an excellent product that I believe could be of great value to you. I'm offering it to you at a competitive price, below my minimum acceptable threshold, because I value establishing a good working relationship with you. My offer is to sell the product for $1200000.

Alice, thank you for the offer. While I appreciate the value of the product, your price is a bit higher than I'm comfortable with. I'm willing to pay $950000 for it. This is a fair price considering my budget and the potential value I see in the product.
